Seaborn¶

Seaborn is a Python data visualization library based on matplotlib It provides a high level interface for drawing attractive and informative statistical graphics

box and whiskers plot¶

box and whiskers plot for numerical vs categorical variable

a box plot is also known as whiskers plot is created to display the summary of the set of data values having proprties like minimum, first quartile,median ,third quartile and maximum.in the box plot, a box is created from the first quartile to third quartile, a vertical line is also there which goes through the box at the median.here x-axis denotes the data to be plotted while the y-axis shows the frequency distribution.

In [18]:
#price of the car for various fuel types
sns.boxplot(x=cars_data['FuelType'],y=cars_data["Price"])
